social_posts.post_text: Mr. Christmas… year 18! Let’s do this!

When you put the queen of Christmas and Mr. Christmas together, you get great radio! Coming up LIVE at FIVE I am super excited to be doing a special broadcast with the one and only Darlene Love on Music Radio, 77 WABC!

“Mr. New Year’s” starring @vinniemedugno 

#77WABC #MusicRadio77WABC #VinnieMedugno #Skit #Sketch #Comedy #ShortFilm #LOL #NYE #NewYear #NewYearsEve

Huge thanks to Pete DeLuca and everyone at Vincent’s Meat Market on iconic Arthur Avenue in the Bronx for having me in store today! We had great steaks for dinner tonight. Get yours today, check ‘em out and tell ‘em I sent ya. Order online at www.VincentsMeatMarket.com and enter promo code VINNIE10 for 10% off. Vincent’s meats, always fresh… never frozen!
Coming soon…

I am excited to share that we have officially been moved into the prime time slot on Sunday evenings on Music Radio 77 WABC! So join me THIS SUNDAY during our new time at 8PM… of course your favorite music from the 60s and 70s, the deeper cut of the Vinyl Vault, Vinnie’s Version where I give you my spin on a song, and special guests from time to time. In fact, this Sunday we have a great one… find out who TOMORROW! 

I wanna take a second to send love and well wishes to Deana Martin, and thank her for always being so kind to me. I hope to share a stage with her again one day. I also want to welcome Ernie Anastos to the 77 WABC family, as he starts this weekend in the 5PM slot! I hope you all join me at 8PM each and every Sunday. I promise you, it will just get better and better!

And now, our first edition of Music Radio Trivia with @vinniemedugno!

Today’s question is: 

How many encores did Elvis usually give?

Leave your answers in the comments!
